      "title": "The Origins of Creation: Generative vs. Discriminative Modeling",
      "scope": "Introduces the foundational goal of generating language rather than just classifying it. We explore the intuition behind modeling the underlying probability distribution of data, setting the stage for the pre-computing era of AI.",
      "concepts": [
